Package: HollywoodMovies2.0
Title: Explore Knn with Hollywood Movies
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Arafath', 'Hossain', email = 'a.h.fahad90@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: This Shiny app demonstrte how K nearest neighbor can be used to group 
  observations based on their features. For demonstration purpose, a dataset of Hollywood movies 
  have been used. Using the app, a user can explore profitability of the movies historically, and 
  decide which movies are closest in nature based on their chosen criteria.
